      "text": "containerd-shim: A tiny process that\nstays alive for every running\ncontainer. It allows the main Docker\nEngine or containerd to restart\nwithout killing your running\ncontainers.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "WTQGgmMHjbQ7jQOOXIrO9",
      "originalText": "containerd-shim: A tiny process that stays alive for every running container. It allows the main Docker Engine or containerd to restart without killing your running containers.",
