      "text": "runc: The low-level \"worker\" that\nactually talks to the Linux kernel\nto create the isolated container\nenvironment. Once the container\nis started, runc exits",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "GA92BMlJ2mBoq2OWlBluq",
      "originalText": "runc: The low-level \"worker\" that actually talks to the Linux kernel to create the isolated container environment. Once the container is started, runc exits",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
