      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "An Image is an immutable\n(unchangeable), read-only file that\nserves as the blueprint for a container.\nIt contains everything your application\nneeds to run, bundled into a single\npackage. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "gPHBQX1uCAsI7-RyfxnHf",
      "originalText": "An Image is an immutable (unchangeable), read-only file that serves as the blueprint for a container. It contains everything your application needs to run, bundled into a single package. ",
